
	libttstd - 	functions for standard interfacing with golinux on
				TomTom devices

libttstd solves generic problems in developing software for TomTom devices
that run golinux.
Currently implemented features are:
	
	- Battery
		provides information about voltage, charge status etc.

	- Framebuffer
		simple interface to the framebuffer device (display) e.g. put a pixel
		on the display, clear the display etc.

	- GPS
		provides GPS-information that is gained from NMEA-Strings parsed with
		nmealib. (latitude, longtitude, satellites in view etc.)

	- Touchscreen
		provides touchscreen information such as x and y position and pressure
				
